sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as MLflow Client<br/>(Python SDK)
    participant KRP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant AuthMW as Auth Middleware<br/>(K8s Auth Provider)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Experiment Tracking (Create Run, Log Metrics)

    Client->>KRP: POST /api/3.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    KRP->>MLflow: Forward (HTTP/localhost)<br/>Proxied Bearer Token
    MLflow->>AuthMW: Authenticate request
    AuthMW->>K8sAPI: TokenReview (validate SA token)<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>AuthMW: Token valid + user info
    AuthMW-->>MLflow: Authenticated (workspace resolved)
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT run record<br/>Workspace-filtered query
    PG-->>MLflow: Run ID
    MLflow-->>KRP: 200 OK (run_id)
    KRP-->>Client: Response (TLS)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Artifact Upload

    Client->>KRP: POST /api/3.0/mlflow/runs/log-artifact<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    KRP->>MLflow: Forward (HTTP/localhost)
    MLflow->>AuthMW: Authenticate + authorize (EDIT permission)
    AuthMW-->>MLflow: Authorized
    MLflow->>S3: PUT object<br/>AWS IAM credentials, TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>MLflow: 200 OK
    MLflow->>PG: UPDATE artifact metadata
    PG-->>MLflow: OK
    MLflow-->>KRP: 200 OK
    KRP-->>Client: Response (TLS)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Workspace Resolution (kubernetes-namespaced)

    Client->>Client: Read /var/run/secrets/.../namespace
    Client->>KRP: GET /api/3.0/mlflow/experiments/search<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>X-MLFLOW-WORKSPACE: {namespace}
    KRP->>MLflow: Forward with workspace header
    MLflow->>AuthMW: Authenticate + resolve workspace
    AuthMW->>K8sAPI: Validate token + namespace access
    K8sAPI-->>AuthMW: Authorized
    MLflow->>PG: SELECT experiments<br/>WHERE workspace = {namespace}
    PG-->>MLflow: Filtered results
    MLflow-->>KRP: 200 OK (experiments)
    KRP-->>Client: Response (TLS)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Web UI Access

    participant Browser as Browser

    Browser->>KRP: GET / (React SPA)<br/>via Platform Gateway HTTPS/443
    KRP->>MLflow: Forward (HTTP/localhost)
    MLflow-->>KRP: index.html + static assets
    KRP-->>Browser: Response (TLS)
    Browser->>KRP: AJAX /ajax-api/3.0/mlflow/experiments/search<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KRP->>MLflow: Forward
    MLflow->>PG: Query experiments
    PG-->>MLflow: Results
    MLflow-->>KRP: JSON response
    KRP-->>Browser: Response (TLS)
